'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2915] on 12 November 2000 at 5:53:16 pm'!"Change Set:		245NewSymbolTable7-sqrDate:			30 August 2000Author:			Andres ValloudSymbol table minor diffs & utility methods.[That's it. Let's cross our fingers that everything works as before :-) --sma]"!!Symbol class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'SqR 8/30/2000 17:04'!compactSymbolTable	"Reduce the size of the symbol table so	that it holds all existing symbols + 1000"	| oldSize |	Smalltalk garbageCollect.	oldSize _ SymbolTable array size.	SymbolTable growTo: SymbolTable size + 1000.	^(oldSize - SymbolTable array size) printString, ' slot(s) reclaimed'! !!Symbol class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'SqR 8/30/2000 17:01'!useHardSymbolTable	SymbolTable _ Set withAll: self allInstances! !!Symbol class methodsFor: 'class initialization' stamp: 'SqR 8/30/2000 17:00'!useWeakSymbolTable	self initialize! !Symbol class removeSelector: #thatDoesNotStart:skipping:!